flowchart TD
    Start([AutoKube System]) --> Phase{Select Phase}
    
    %% PHASE 1: DATA COLLECTION
    Phase -->|Phase 1| P1Start[Data Collection]
    P1Start --> InitDC[Initialize Data Collector]
    InitDC --> StartTimer[Start 5min Timer]
    
    StartTimer --> Collect[Collect Unified Data]
    Collect --> GetPods[List All Pods]
    GetPods --> GetMetrics[Query Prometheus Metrics]
    GetMetrics --> GetLogs[Fetch Pod Logs]
    GetLogs --> ParseLogs[Parse Errors & Requests]
    
    ParseLogs --> Merge[Merge Metrics + Logs]
    Merge --> Enrich[Add Pod Metadata]
    Enrich --> Label{Labeling Logic}
    
    Label -->|High Error Rate| Unhealthy[Mark: IsHealthy=false]
    Label -->|High CPU/Memory| Unhealthy
    Label -->|Frequent Restarts| Unhealthy
    Label -->|Normal Behavior| Healthy[Mark: IsHealthy=true]
    
    Unhealthy --> WriteCSV[Append to CSV]
    Healthy --> WriteCSV
    WriteCSV --> LogSuccess[Log: N points collected]
    LogSuccess --> Wait1[Wait 5 minutes]
    Wait1 --> Collect
    
    %% PHASE 2: ML TRAINING
    Phase -->|Phase 2| P2Start[ML Training]
    P2Start --> LoadData[Load Training Dataset]
    LoadData --> ValidateData{Sufficient Data?}
    ValidateData -->|No| WaitMore[Wait for more data]
    WaitMore --> LoadData
    ValidateData -->|Yes| FeatureEng[Feature Engineering]
    
    FeatureEng --> SplitData[Train/Test Split]
    SplitData --> TrainModel[Train IsolationForest]
    TrainModel --> Evaluate[Evaluate Model]
    Evaluate --> CheckPerf{Performance OK?}
    
    CheckPerf -->|No| TuneParams[Tune Hyperparameters]
    TuneParams --> TrainModel
    CheckPerf -->|Yes| SaveModel[Save Model to Storage]
    SaveModel --> NotifyDevs[Notify DevOps Team]
    
    %% PHASE 3: SELF-HEALING
    Phase -->|Phase 3| P3Start[Self-Healing Controller]
    P3Start --> LoadModel[Load Trained Model]
    LoadModel --> InitCtrl[Initialize Controller]
    InitCtrl --> MonitorLoop[Start Monitor Loop]
    
    MonitorLoop --> ObserveState[Observe Cluster State]
    ObserveState --> CollectCurrent[Get Current Metrics & Logs]
    CollectCurrent --> BuildVector[Build State Vector]
    BuildVector --> Predict[Predict with ML Model]
    
    Predict --> Analyze{Anomaly Detected?}
    
    Analyze -->|No Anomaly| ContinueMonitor[Continue Monitoring]
    ContinueMonitor --> Wait2[Wait 30 seconds]
    Wait2 --> ObserveState
    
    Analyze -->|Anomaly Found| SelectAction{Select Healing Action}
    
    SelectAction -->|High Error Rate| RestartPod[Restart Pod]
    SelectAction -->|Resource Spike| ScaleUp[Scale Deployment Up]
    SelectAction -->|Memory Leak| RestartPod
    SelectAction -->|Performance Degr.| Rollback[Rollback Deployment]
    
    RestartPod --> ExecuteK8s[Execute via K8s API]
    ScaleUp --> ExecuteK8s
    Rollback --> ExecuteK8s
    
    ExecuteK8s --> LogAction[Log Healing Action]
    LogAction --> AlertDevs[Alert DevOps if Critical]
    AlertDevs --> Wait2
    
    %% Styling
    style P1Start fill:#4A90E2,color:#fff
    style P2Start fill:#9B59B6,color:#fff
    style P3Start fill:#E67E22,color:#fff
    style Unhealthy fill:#E74C3C,color:#fff
    style Healthy fill:#2ECC71,color:#fff
    style WriteCSV fill:#27AE60,color:#fff
    style SaveModel fill:#F39C12,color:#fff
    style RestartPod fill:#E67E22,color:#fff
    style ScaleUp fill:#3498DB,color:#fff
